high_descs: Walk slightly to the right towards the round white table and turn right at the cabinet. walk straight pass the cabinet, turn slightly to the left and turn left again to go to the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter top next to the stove.
Turn right, walk straight towards the white round table, turn right after the cabinet and walk straight to the white table.
Cut the bread near the window using the knife.
Walk to the left to the trash can on the other side of the room.
put the knife in the trash can.
Go back to the round white table at the other side of the room.
Get a slice of the bread that you cut from the table.
Go slightly to the left, turn left, walk towards the door and turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bread on the rack, close the fridge, let it cool for a few seconds, pick up the bread again and close the door.
Walk back to the trash can again.
Put the cold bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bread in the trash can

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the white round table on the opposite side.
Slice the bread behind the two white cups closer to the edge of the table.
Turn left and go to the trash can at the end of the counter.
Place the gray knife in the trash can.
Turn around and go back to the white round table.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on the opposite side of the kitchen.
Chill the bread in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn right to go to the trash can at the end of the counter.
Place the chilled bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a chilled slice of bread in the trash can

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk back across the kitchen, when you reach the end of the counter turn right and walk to the front of the table so that you are facing the window.
Cut the loaf of bread on the table, all the way in the back, behind the two white cups, into slices.
Turn to your left and walk to the garbage can across from you.
Place the knife in the garbage can, on the floor.
Turn to your left and walk back to the table the sliced bread is on.
Pick up the end slice of bread, closest to you, on the table.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the stove, then make a right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the slice of bread on the top shelf, in front of the white cup, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for the bread to chill, then remove the bread from the refrigerator.
Tum to your right and walk across the kitchen, then turn right at the end of the counter and go to the garbage can on the floor.
Toss the piece of bread in the garbage can, against the kitchen cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in the garbage can.
